VI. THE TWO ROUTES TO THE CURE (set up here, chosen later)
=====================================================================
Saijah's eventual patron choice IS the party's strategy for the Eldergleam:
  - KYNARETH ROUTE: heal the true heart. REQUIRES DANICA (Section VII). The
    slow, social, merciful road.
  - HIRCINE ROUTE: needs NO Danica at all. Saijah becomes the Alpha and they
    CULL — tear the corruption out by the root with apex-predator force. Fast,
    brutal, amputation, and it costs Saijah her Kynareth-self.
So if the Danica reconciliation looks impossible, Hircine's road becomes the
tempting shortcut — pay with Saijah's soul instead of Davinia's pride. Plant
the existence of BOTH routes here; force NEITHER.

